tags: how deep in the phandom do you have to be to consider their privacy in a dream
summary: I had a dream that I was helping Dan propose to Phil. But out of respect for their privacy, I left the room when it was actually...
body:
I had a dream that I was helping Dan propose to Phil. But out of respect for their privacy, I left the room when it was actually happening. When I came back, I didn’t even ask “Did he say yes?”. Because obviously he would. They didn’t mention it, but they did hold hands when we watched a movie together. I was tempted to post something online about it but knew that would be wrong since I didn’t ask them first.

Edit: I’ve thought about this a lot today. And honestly, how am I so deep in the phandom I dream about my otp proposing, but I’m too concerned with their right to privacy to even let myself see it or talk about it.
